      <title>時尚集團愛馬仕 (Hermes) 誓言針對柏金 (Birkin) 訴訟“大力辯護”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/fashion-group-hermes-vows-vigorously-defend-itself-against-birkin-lawsuit-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[時尚公司愛馬仕 (Hermes) 在加州提起的訴訟中誓言要“大力捍衛自己”，稱該公司非法只允許在該公司有“足夠購買歷史”的顧客購買其著名的柏金包 (Birkin) 手袋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/fashion-group-hermes-vows-vigorously-defend-itself-against-birkin-lawsuit-2024-04-30/</guid>
